l McCann will also be taking part in the public event at Conway Square in Newtownards this evening.\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 897, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachel_McCann\", \"score\": 0.9999978234251143, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rachel McCann\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachel_McCann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachel_McCann\"}, {\"begin\": 976, \"end\": 987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newtownards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.29098452155626e-26, \"text\": \"Newtownards\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newtownards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newtownards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This has been Northern Ireland's most successful Olympic Games, with athletes from the region winning a record seven medals, including four gold in Paris.\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1017, \"end\": 1033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999998331077, \"rank\": 1.5703312104406028e-10, \"text\": \"Northern Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 1151, \"end\": 1156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995404583534, \"rank\": 4.5954178204955e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Homecoming events have already taken place for gold and bronze medallist swimmer Daniel Wiffen on Tuesday evening in Magheralin and for gold medallist rower Hannah Scott on Wednesday in Coleraine.\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1276, \"end\": 1286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Magheralin\", \"score\": 0.9999999999965894, \"rank\": 2.321082361